Package api

Class OTM

  • java.lang.Object
    • api.OTM
  • public class OTM
extends Object
    Public API. The methods in the API are of three types. Basic scenario loading and running methods belong to the OTM class. Methods for querying and modifying a scenario belong to api.Network. Methods for requesting outputs and calculating different metrics are in api.Output.
